# Tabula agent workflow

Compliance domain umbrella. Primary product: **fstec** (`fstec/` submodule).

## Context

- Work inside `fstec/` for product changes — follow fstec AGENTS/plans
- GUI primitives come from cxado `shared/gui` (`@cxado/gui`)
- Tabula repo holds domain docs and submodule wiring only

## Branches

`tabula/phase-NN-<slug>` for umbrella changes; fstec uses `fstec/*` branches.

## Verify (fstec)

```bash
cd fstec && npm run typecheck && npm run build
```

Core rules: symlinked via `make rules-link` from cxado meta-repo.
